{"tid":2367104,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"七旬翁損毀鄭麗琼議辦海報獲撤控 准簽保守行為 賠償兩元","createTime":"2021-01-15T05:28:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-16T04:30:42.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":60,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"583a4e5be8ba5838c49c8519085c83f5cbf3261c","tid":2367104,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T05:28:47.000Z","msg":"七旬翁去年6月途經中西區區議會主席鄭麗琼辦事處，用傘篤兩張印有「毋忘六四」及「無懼打壓」字句的海報，被控一項刑事損毀罪。案件今早再訊，控方同意撤銷控罪，讓涉事老翁以2,000元簽保守行為18個月結案，並賠償2元了事。<br />\n<br />\n報稱退休的被告楊國輝（71歲），被控於去年6月8日在中環堅道134號A舖鄭麗琼議員辦事處，損壞兩張印有「毋忘六四 人心不死」及「無懼打壓 戰鬥到底」字樣的海報。<br />\n<br />\n案情指，去年6月8日下午2時半，事主在案發地點貼上兩張海報，惟兩小時後發現部份海報甩脫，翻看閉路電視，發現有不知名老翁於3時許用傘篤海報，其後進入堅道128-132號堅威大廈。警員向保安查問，獲知老翁為該大廈立案法團秘書。警員其後看見被告以同樣服飾再度出現，上前拘捕。警誡下被告承認用傘撩甩海報。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210115/TEGCLWKYCFBZNECDVPD5DSXT4E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210115%2FTEGCLWKYCFBZNECDVPD5DSXT4E%2F&d=ZtPc16BOUua4x2eUEWBZFvsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=25174935\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210115%2FTEGCLWKYCFBZNECDVPD5DSXT4E%2F&h=a42fb025\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210115/TEGCLWKYCFBZNECDVPD5DSXT4E/</a>"},{"pid":"fd8fa05faa4b829d5a24ec0f5154c33dac752fdd","tid":2367104,"uid":79563,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T05:29:27.000Z","msg":"賠償兩元 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我幫佢比得唔得？"},{"pid":"4351319c3de1d34889ecd8cd3371c77782c538bc","tid":2367104,"uid":43062,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T05:29:54.000Z","msg":"屌你用黎搭車呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3318cd3352f879aeee349c962a0d9e14d156060","tid":2367104,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T05:30:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"